00:04:24.510 --> 00:04:28.520
and it was based on this very
important Supreme Court decision.

00:04:28.520 --> 00:04:30.370
How many of you have
heard of the Lovings?

00:04:30.370 --> 00:04:36.010
The adults say yes, so we're
hoping before this morning is over,

00:04:36.010 --> 00:04:40.220
we would have educated
the students here today.

00:04:40.220 --> 00:04:43.820
Believe it or not, there was
a time in American history

00:04:43.820 --> 00:04:49.530
that white Americans and African
Americans could not get married.

00:04:49.530 --> 00:04:51.700
I know it's very hard to wrap
your head around that nowadays,

00:04:51.700 --> 00:04:54.690
but that was a dark
time in this history,

00:04:54.690 --> 00:04:58.390
and you could've been thrown in
jail if a couple got married.

00:04:58.390 --> 00:05:00.100
That's what happened
with the Lovings.

00:05:00.100 --> 00:05:04.620
Mildred Jeter, who was black, and
Richard Loving, who was white,

00:05:04.620 --> 00:05:07.220
lived in not-so-far Virginia.

00:05:07.220 --> 00:05:09.860
They got married here in
Washington, and when they went home

00:05:09.860 --> 00:05:13.130
to Central Point, they were
arrested and sentenced to a year

00:05:13.130 --> 00:05:15.780
in prison just because
they were married.

00:05:15.780 --> 00:05:18.430
Yes, really hard to
imagine that now.

00:05:18.430 --> 00:05:20.900
Their case went all the
way to the Supreme Court,

00:05:20.900 --> 00:05:24.360
and 50 years ago this
year, they won.

00:05:24.360 --> 00:05:26.320
Their case changed the
law across the country

00:05:26.320 --> 00:05:30.600
so that one's race does not
determine who one can marry.

00:05:30.600 --> 00:05:33.080
The story has just been published

00:05:33.080 --> 00:05:35.800
in a new book called
Loving vs. Virginia.

00:05:35.800 --> 00:05:38.350
We have the author here
today, Patricia Hruby Powell,

00:05:38.350 --> 00:05:43.170
and the book's illustrator Shadra
Strickland who's joined us here

00:05:43.170 --> 00:05:44.470
on the stage.

00:05:44.470 --> 00:05:48.000
