adults who want to marry,

00:36:02.620 --> 00:36:06.810
to deny that right on the basis
of race is unconstitutional.

00:36:06.810 --> 00:36:08.530
It interferes with
the fundamental right

00:36:08.530 --> 00:36:13.310
and it makes a classification
based on race which is not allowed

00:36:13.310 --> 00:36:14.820
under the 14th amendment.

00:36:14.820 --> 00:36:17.400
